# Wisp Tauri

- PTY via portable-pty; one blocking reader thread per session
- Stream output via Tauri Channel<Vec<u8>>; input via write_terminal command
- Fish resolver in shell.rs: which + platform paths, spawn fish -l
- Env: TERM=xterm-256color, COLORTERM=truecolor
- TerminalManager holds HashMap<Uuid, PtySession>; cleanup on tab close
